OL,3,CLearning disabled adults face care
OL,4,Ccuts after 'unsafe assessments', say
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FITV News visited two learning disabled
OL,8,Fadults, Matthew (left) and Phillip
OL,9,F(right), who are facing devastating
OL,10,Fcuts to their support hours after a
OL,11,F"negligent" assessment process, claim
OL,12,Ftheir families and care provider.
OL,14,FWatch Political Correspondent Romilly
OL,15,FWeeks' report, produced by Elisa
OL,16,FMenendez.
OL,18,FDozens of learning disabled and
OL,19,Fautistic adults are facing "dangerous"
OL,20,Fcut backs to their care, ITV News has
OL,21,Ffound.
