OL,4,Ccuts after 'unsafe assessments', say
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FSurrey County Council has been accused
OL,8,Fof carrying out "illegal" and
OL,9,F"immoral" care assessments of
OL,10,Fvulnerable adults, and excluding their
OL,11,Ffamilies, in a bid to save money by
OL,12,Freducing their support.
OL,14,FCare provider Peak15 said 27 learning
OL,15,Fdisabled adults in supported living
OL,16,Fare facing average cuts of almost 50%
OL,17,Fto their care hours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/32
