OL,7,FIn almost all of the cases, vital
OL,8,Fmental capacity assessments were not
OL,9,Fcarried out to determine whether the
OL,10,Freduction in their care hours was safe.
OL,12,FA mental capacity assessment
OL,13,Festablishes whether someone has the
OL,14,Fability to make decisions about their
OL,15,Fown safety and wellbeing, and helps
OL,16,Fdetermine what support they may need.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/32
