OL,4,Ccuts after 'unsafe assessments', say
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FThe government is considering changing
OL,8,Fthe law to give families the right to
OL,9,Frequest a mental capacity assessment
OL,10,Ffor a vulnerable loved one, as
OL,11,Freported by ITV News. It follows years
OL,12,Fof campaigning by Fiona Laskaris who
OL,13,Fbelieves this key legislative change
OL,14,Fcould have saved her autistic son,
OL,15,FChristopher, who was murdered in his
OL,16,Fown home after authorities failed to
OL,17,Fgive him an assessment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/32
