OL,7,FSurrey County Council's accounts make
OL,8,Fclear its intention to save #2.2
OL,9,Fmillion on their spending on supported
OL,10,Fliving for those with learning
OL,11,Fdisabilities and autism in 2025/26.
OL,13,F'Almost going back to long-stay
OL,14,Finstitutions where we're just
OL,15,Fwarehousing people because it's cheap'
OL,17,FPeak15's chairman David Holmes
OL,18,Fbelieves Surrey's savings target
OL,19,Fplayed a role in the assessment
OL,20,Fprocess, which he describes as
OL,21,F"flawed" and "negligent".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/32
