OL,7,FMental capacity assessments are a
OL,8,F"really important step" in that
OL,9,Fprocess but they "by and large weren't
OL,10,Fundertaken", he told ITV News.
OL,12,F"And what that meant is that people's
OL,13,Ffamilies were excluded and that as a
OL,14,Fcare provider we were excluded from
OL,15,Fthat process," David said, adding that
OL,16,F17 of the adults under his care have
OL,17,Fno family to advocate for them.
OL,19,F"It meant that the people that know
OL,20,Fthose individuals well were excluded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/32
