OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FApart from helping with the day-to-day
OL,8,Fbasics, Peak15 also takes learning
OL,9,Fdisabled adults to art classes,
OL,10,Fwalking groups and even down to the
OL,11,Fpub. All of that, along with vital
OL,12,Fsupport with showering, cooking and
OL,13,Fcleaning, will likely disappear under
OL,14,Fthe proposed cuts.
OL,16,F"We want to support people to live a
OL,17,Flife. We want people to be out there
OL,18,Fin the community, building
OL,19,Frelationships, getting jobs, finding
OL,20,Flove," said David.
