OL,7,FIt took Linda months of emails and
OL,8,Ftelephone calls to get a copy of his
OL,9,Fassessment, she said, and that when
OL,10,Fshe did, it was full of "glaringly
OL,11,Fobvious" inaccuracies.
OL,13,F"What Surrey are proposing is just not
OL,14,Fgoing to work, it's dangerous," she
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FAsked how she would start to tell him
OL,18,Fthat the life he's known and
OL,19,Feverything he relies on is being taken
OL,20,Faway, Linda said Phillip wouldn't be
OL,21,Fable to comprehend what was happening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/32
