OL,7,F"He would know people were
OL,8,Fdisappearing from his life and 'why
OL,9,Fare people no longer wanting to be
OL,10,Fwith me and work with me and do things
OL,11,Fwith me and take me out to the cinema
OL,12,Fand take me down to the pub once a
OL,13,Fweek for a pint?' All that would stop.
OL,14,FCan you imagine?"
OL,16,FShe said the majority of his life
OL,17,Fwould just be confined to his room,
OL,18,Fhaving no meaningful interactions with
OL,19,Fothers.
