OL,3,CLearning disabled adults face care
OL,4,Ccuts after 'unsafe assessments', say
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,F"It took the staff a long time to get
OL,8,Fhim settled in. For a long period of
OL,9,Ftime he would only stay in his room
OL,10,Fhiding in a wardrobe. It took a lot of
OL,11,Fpatience and dedication to get him to
OL,12,Fcome and mix with other people and
OL,13,Feventually to start going out."
OL,15,FNow, Matthew enjoys a full life going
OL,16,Fto weekly art classes, cooking classes
OL,17,Fand ramble groups, and is supported
OL,18,Fdaily by care workers - but that could
OL,19,Fbe under threat after Surrey
OL,20,Freassessed him without his brother
OL,21,FAndrew there.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/32
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
