OL,3,CLearning disabled adults face care
OL,4,Ccuts after 'unsafe assessments', say
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,F"I don't think his capacity was fully
OL,8,Fconsidered because he can't read or
OL,9,Fwrite. He can't really communicate his
OL,10,Fneeds properly. So he needs more
OL,11,Fsupport at the meeting," Andrew said.
OL,13,F"And I don't know what happened to
OL,14,Fthat assessment when it was written up
OL,15,Fbecause it wasn't given to me and it
OL,16,Fwasn't given to Peak 15. And it
OL,17,Fcouldn't have been given to Matthew
OL,18,Fbecause he couldn't understand it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/32
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
