OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,F"So the decision to cut his hours was
OL,8,Fdone really behind our backs and it
OL,9,Fwasn't transparent at all.
OL,11,F"And I think it's quite unfair and
OL,12,Fseems to just be to save money at the
OL,13,Fexpense of some of the most vulnerable
OL,14,Fpeople in Surrey's care."
OL,16,FSince we filmed with Matthew, Surrey
OL,17,FCounty Council has offered him a re-
OL,18,Fassessment of his needs with Andrew
OL,19,Fpresent following a complaint.
