OL,4,Ccuts after 'unsafe assessments', say
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FHis mother Fiona Laskaris - backed by
OL,8,FDorking and Horley Lib Dem MP Chris
OL,9,FCoghlan - has been working with the
OL,10,Fgovernment on "Christopher's Law",
OL,11,Fwhich would mean authorities would
OL,12,Fhave a duty to carry out such
OL,13,Fassessments.
OL,15,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,16,Fspokesperson told ITV News it will be
OL,17,Fupdating the code of practice on the
OL,18,FMental Capacity Act this year.
