OL,7,FThey said: "This government is
OL,8,Fdetermined to support SEND families
OL,9,Fand those with learning disabilities
OL,10,Fto get the care they need. That's why,
OL,11,Fwe are working closely with Fiona
OL,12,FLaskaris to examine what further
OL,13,Faction we can take to prevent further
OL,14,Ftragedies, following the tragic death
OL,15,Fof her son.
