OL,7,F"We will be consulting on liberty
OL,8,Fprotection safeguards this year, which
OL,9,Fwill include an updated Code of
OL,10,FPractice for the Mental Capacity Act,
OL,11,Fand welcome Fiona's feedback as part
OL,12,Fof that process"
OL,14,FExperts, including the National
OL,15,FAutistic Society, agree that the
OL,16,Fcurrent system is failing autistic
OL,17,Fadults like Christopher, as well as
OL,18,Fother adults with learning
OL,19,Fdisabilities and mental health
OL,20,Fillnesses, at times with catastrophic
OL,21,Fconsequences.
