OL,7,FSinead Mooney, Surrey County Council's
OL,8,FCabinet Member for Adult Social Care,
OL,9,Fsaid: "We're absolutely committed to
OL,10,Fmaking sure that people get the right
OL,11,Fsupport to meet their needs and build
OL,12,Ftheir independence - and far from
OL,13,Fcutting costs, we're increasing
OL,14,Finvestment in adult social care in
OL,15,FSurrey, despite financial pressures
OL,16,Ffacing local councils. We've just
OL,17,Fapproved an adult social care budget
OL,18,Fincrease of more than #27million.
