OL,7,F"Care Act assessments are carried out
OL,8,Fby qualified professionals in line
OL,9,Fwith our legal duties, with decisions
OL,10,Fbased on evidence rather than targets,
OL,11,Fand we also consider bringing in
OL,12,Fothers close to the individual.
OL,14,F"We won't comment on individual cases,
OL,15,Fbut if someone feels their assessment
OL,16,Fdoesn't fully reflect their situation,
OL,17,Fwe encourage them to contact us
OL,18,Fdirectly and we'll urgently consider
OL,19,Fif a reassessment is needed.
